<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Relationship Contract 💍</title>

<style>
body{
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffdde1, #ee9ca7);
    margin:0;
    padding:20px;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
}

.container{
    background:white;
    width:100%;
    max-width:700px;
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:20px;
}

/* TEXT ONLY — NO WORD CHANGES */
h1, p{
    margin:10px 0;
}

/* ALIGNMENT FIX */
.option{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:10px;
    margin:5px 0;
}

/* CIRCLE BUTTON */
.option input[type="radio"]{
    appearance:none;
    width:18px;
    height:18px;
    border:2px solid #ff4d6d;
    border-radius:50%;
    cursor:pointer;
    position:relative;
    flex-shrink:0;
}

.option input[type="radio"]:checked{
    background:#ff4d6d;
}

/* INPUT TEXT AREAS */
textarea{
    width:100%;
    padding:8px;
    border-radius:8px;
    border:1px solid #ccc;
}

input[type="text"], input[type="number"], input[type="date"], input[type="email"]{
    width:100%;
    padding:8px;
    margin-top:5px;
    border-radius:8px;
    border:1px solid #ccc;
}

.section{
    margin-top:20px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>💍 RELATIONSHIP CONTRACT 💍</h1>

<p>First Name: ___________________</p>
<p>Middle Name: ___________________</p>
<p>Last Name: ___________________</p>
<p>Age: ___________________</p>
<p>Birthday: ___________________</p>
<p>Gmail: ___________________</p>
<p>Contact Number: ___________________</p>
<p>Date Today: ___________________</p>

<p>☑ Terms and Conditions Agreed</p>

<hr>

<p>📜 PROMISE SECTION 📜</p>

<p>Do you promise to be my partner in life?</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q1"> Yes</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q1"> Of course</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q1"> Why not?</div>

<p>Will you take care of me for the rest of my life?</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q2"> yes</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q2"> of course</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q2"> always</div>

<p>Do you promise to not hurt me? such as, cheating.</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q3"> yes</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q3"> I would never cheat on you</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q3"> I'm loyal</div>

<p>Will you reply even when you are asleep?</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q4"> Yes</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q4"> Yeah</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q4"> Yep</div>

<p>Do you promise not to disappear during arguments?</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q5"> I promise</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q5"> I swear</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q5"> Of course, why not baby</div>

<p>Do you promise to always come back to me, only me, me me me meeee</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q6"> BIG YESSS</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q6"> ALWAYYSSSS</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="q6"> I PROMISEEEE</div>

<hr>

<p>💗 PERSONAL QUESTIONS 💗</p>

<p>Do you see me as your future wife?</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p1"> Yes</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p1"> No</div>

<p>Do you truly love me?</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p2"> Yes</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p2"> no</div>

<p>Will you burn the world for me?</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p3"> Yes</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p3"> No</div>

<p>Will you kill yourself or anyone just for me?</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p4"> Yes</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p4"> No</div>

<p>Do you trust me tho? Be honest.</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p5"> Yes</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p5"> No</div>
<p>message: (THERE'S AN OPTIONAL TEXT HER)</p>

<p>Am I annoying?</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p6"> Yes</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p6"> No</div>
<p>message: (an optional text/message)</p>

<p>Will you stay through highs and lows?</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p7"> Yes</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p7"> No</div>

<p>Will you be my husband?</p>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p8"> -Yes</div>
<div class="option"><input type="radio" name="p8"> -No</div>

<hr>

<p>📝 ESSAY SECTION 📝</p>

<p>Will you choose me over your greatest love?</p>
<textarea></textarea>

<p>How about your mom? HAHAHAHA</p>
<textarea></textarea>

<p>Will you stay even if I’m being too much and hard to handle?</p>
<textarea></textarea>

<p>Will you still love me if I was a worm?</p>
<textarea></textarea>

<p>A dinosaur? ror</p>
<textarea></textarea>

<p>Describe me:</p>
<textarea></textarea>

<p>What do you love about me?</p>
<textarea></textarea>

<hr>

<p>⚠️ CONSEQUENCE SECTION ⚠️</p>

<p>Stay faithful and loyal. If you break this contract, choose your consequence below</p>

<p>- Cut off your “dih”</p>

<p>Penalty for making me sulk:</p>
<p>-send me a dih</p>

<p>🎉 FINAL RESULT 🎉</p>

<p>Now that it’s settled, we are officially unofficially married 💖😂</p>

</div>

</body>
</html>
